cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use NullShift in your research, tools, or publications, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "NullShift"
abstract: >
  An open-source AI-powered triage assistant for L1 SOC analysts.
  NullShift plugs into your SIEM, retrieves the right playbook for each
  alert via RAG, runs deterministic investigation steps, enriches IOCs
  against threat intelligence, and produces a structured investigation
  report (Section 1 evidence, Section 2 reasoning, Section 3 verdict).
  Provider-agnostic LLM layer supporting Claude Agent SDK, 15+ cloud
  providers, and fully local Ollama. Built-in connectors for Wazuh,
  LimaCharlie, Splunk, Elastic, and Microsoft Sentinel.
